{"tid":2266423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解d人只係會話武肺死亡率低，但冇諗過傳染力高直接會令到死亡人數增加？","createTime":"2020-11-01T10:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T10:19:50.000Z","uid":140953,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"218d58014cef13b3576986ac118266f8dfef03e6","tid":2266423,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"見到d反口罩、當依d病係細病既人成日話依隻病死亡率低<br />\n但點解從來都唔會諗下傳染力高，就算死亡率低最終一樣會死好多人？<br />\n<br />\n病毒A：傳染率1%，死亡率30%<br />\n病毒B：傳染率30%、死亡率1%<br />\n兩隻病最終死亡人數係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係因為病毒B死亡率低就冇事<br />\n正如武肺一樣，死亡率低但因為傳染力極高，最後死亡人數都係會多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db977d7db604b62f725a50e67899cc1dd62f861b","tid":2266423,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"So?<br />\n<br />\nD高危人仕係唔係都就快死㗎喎"},{"pid":"c09b3bf396f4914fcec692e133396dd641e27eb2","tid":2266423,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"但專家 主流媒體普遍淨係提確診數同死亡數，死亡/康復率就唔提"},{"pid":"79e81db8f0d7c7c64b03a488ecf67fd4016cbfb3","tid":2266423,"uid":140953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db977d7db604b62f725a50e67899cc1dd62f861b","tid":2266423,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"So?<br />\n<br />\nD高危人仕係唔係都就快死㗎喎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:04:30.000Z","msg":"咁不如安樂死哂所有高危人士好唔好？"},{"pid":"548eb0a4ce18f12ccb34d036ed433f45b569d989","tid":2266423,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79e81db8f0d7c7c64b03a488ecf67fd4016cbfb3","tid":2266423,"uid":140953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db977d7db604b62f725a50e67899cc1dd62f861b","tid":2266423,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"So?<br />\n<br />\nD高危